==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''Moksha'''

# A language of the [[Fennic]] branch of the [[Uralic]] language family, spoken by about 428,000 people in the western and southern parts of [[Mordovia]], an independent republic within [[Russia]], and the adjacent regions of Tambov, Penza, Samara, Ulyanovsk, Saratov, Tatarstan, Buguruslan and Bashkortostan.

